descriptions: You can download a trial version of this app to try it for 15 minutes for free.
You won’t be charged anything when this free trial ends. You can’t make in-app purchases or use add-on content during this free trial, but you’ll keep any achievements you earn.

display_long_description:
# Strap chickens to your gun, blast eggs at evil targets and rule the island! 🐔💥 Join the wacky arcade chaos now – The Eggspenders is live in Early Access!

🐔 **Cluck n'load**

Strap in your chicken and unleash a storm of egg-blasting chaos!

[media]

🥚 **Early Access**

Join now—the island is just hatching, and more surprises are on the way!
